id: pm-vb5a
title: "ADR: Two extension-authoring idioms: defineExtension (package mode) vs import-free JSDoc (extension-only)"
description: "Two extension-authoring idioms: defineExtension (package mode) vs import-free JSDoc (extension-only)"
